  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Make the Christmas of Elderly People Special</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Pakistan, the lack of social protection to elderly people (age 60-85) makes them extremely vulnerable in the family and societal structures. At average, there is one elderly person in each residing family of Pakistan and they are treated as burden in majority of the families. A Small Christmas Package can make their Christmas special. AWARD will provide Surprise Christmas Packages to 150 elderly people whose hope for happiness and care are vanishing.</narrative>
  </description>
